```class Solution {
    public int distanceTraveled(int mainTank, int additionalTank) {
        int totalDistance = 0;
        while (mainTank > 0 || additionalTank > 0) {
            int distance = Math.min(mainTank, 5);
            totalDistance += distance * 10;
            mainTank -= distance;
            if (mainTank < 5 && additionalTank > 0) {
                mainTank += 1;
                additionalTank -= 1;
            }
        }
        return totalDistance;
    }
}```
